name: THE TICKLE - Issue #27 - Trippelcover (Guandanarian edition)
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

Issue #27 features artists Sutu Eats Flies (@sutu_eats_flies), Jana Trautmann (@Nnamtuart1) & Guandanarian (@Guandanarian), with a short story by Rebecca Jagoe (@Rebecca84807734).

Created by artist Wily Guys (@guyswily) with help from Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier) and Joanne Rush (@JonicolaRush)
